      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "DRACENA (6) resumes here but has a win and a second from three first-up attempts and has revved up for this with two recent trials. Handles all going and should be right there when the whips are cracking. LADY LUCIFER (4) is one from one over this track and trip, strips fitter second-up from the break and gets some weight relief with the 2kg claim. Plenty to like about her prospects. HERMIONE PRANCER (9) put back-to-back wins together before the spell and looks the runner in this field with the most upside. Include in calculations while fresh. HOLY FLASH (7) saves his best form for this distance range and will be cherry-ripe for this. Shapes as one to consider. BOLLINGER MISS (8) next best with Maloney on top.",
